Besides the previous parameters that were described with one letter, we have 
discovered with our evaluation that some other parameters are useless in terms of 
semantic annotation processes, since they refer to the navigation process through the 
RESTful service results. This is the case, for example, of parameters like: page, total, 
hits, etc. We are planning to discard these types of input parameters in the future.
